'''圣方济各沙勿略堂'''（San Francesco Saverio）是一座[[巴洛克|巴洛克]]风格的[[罗马天主教|罗马天主教]]教堂，位于意大利[[里米尼|里米尼]]法拉利广场12号。

==历史==
这座教堂是由[[耶稣会|耶稣会]]建于1721年。<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=DrA7AQAAIAAJ Guida del forestiere nella città di Rimini] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=DrA7AQAAIAAJ |date=20160505090816 }}, by Luigi Tonini, 1864, page 23.</ref><ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=OlxEAQAAMAAJ La patria; geografia dell' Italia: pte. 2. Provincie di Ravenna, Ferrara, Forli'] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=OlxEAQAAMAAJ |date=20161222083640 }}, Luigi Borsari, 1901, page 279 and 281.</ref>。

布局仿照罗马[[耶稣教堂|耶稣教堂]]。内部装饰华丽。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.riminiturismo.it/visitatori/scopri-il-territorio/arte-e-cultura/chiese/chiesa-del-suffragio | title = Rimini Turismo | publisher = entry | access-date = 2016-04-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160407005114/http://www.riminiturismo.it/visitatori/scopri-il-territorio/arte-e-cultura/chiese/chiesa-del-suffragio | archive-date = 2016-04-07 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>毗邻的耶稣会修道院，曾改为医院多年，现为博物馆。

